1.Creating a Git Repository

Q.How to initialize a new Git repository.
Ans. git init

Q.How to clone an existing repository.
Ans.git clone <url>

Assignment: Create a new repository named my-first-repo and initialize it.
Solution:   mkdir gitworkshop25mayassignment
            cd gitworkshop25mayassignment
            mkdir myfirst-repo
            cd myfirst-repo
            git init

